<div class="home-container" id="how-it-works">
  <h3 class="text-center">How We Work</h3>

  <div class="center mt-5 mb-2">
    <div>
      <div class="box-container">
        <p class="number">1</p>
        <strong>Submit your essay</strong><br>Click <%= link_to "Submit an Essay", new_essay_path %>, give us your details, and upload your latest draft! The price of our service is based on application type (undergraduate or graduate) and length of your essay (word limit). Check out our pricing details <%= link_to "here", "#pricing" %>.
      </div>
      <div class="box-container">
        <p class="number">2</p>
        <strong>Meet your editor</strong><br>Over email, we'll introduce you to the editor who will be helping you reveal your best self on paper. All our editors are experienced essay specialists, carefully vetted and trained to deliver thorough and comprehensive reviews.
      </div>
      <div class="box-container">
        <p class="number">3</p>
        <strong>Receive feedback</strong><br>Within 2-3 working days, receive a complete review of your essay. Each review will include feedback on essay concept, structure, content, and of course, corrections to spelling and grammar. 100% error-free guarantee.
      </div>
      <div class="box-container">
        <p class="number">4</p>
        <strong>Finalize your essay</strong><br>Engage in a one-on-one working session with your editor to finalize your essay. Here, you'll get the chance to clarify, discuss, and collaboratively incorporate feedback received to ensure your essay is submission-ready.
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="center">
    <%= link_to "Submit an Essay!", new_essay_path, class: "main-btn" %>
  </div>
</div>

